      "span_text": "Studies with another retrovirus using a À1 ribosomal frameshift to synthesize Gag-Pol, the equine infectious anemia virus indicated that mutations that reduced frameshift efficiency by as much as 50% continued to sustain viral replication, but that greater reductions in frameshifting efficiency led to replication defects"
